'''加泰羅尼亞之路'''（{{lang-ca|''Via Catalana''}}），又稱加泰羅尼亞通往獨立之路（{{lang|ca|''Via Catalana cap a la Independència''}}），是由加泰羅尼亞國家大會提出并实施的一个400公里長的[[人鏈|人鏈]]活动，以爭取[[加泰羅尼亞獨立運動|加泰羅尼亞獨立]]。此次活动於[[加泰羅尼亞民族日|加泰羅尼亞民族日]]，即2013年9月11日舉行<ref name=wsj>{{cite news|last=Moffett|first=Matt|title=Catalan Separatists to Link for Independence Cause|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324324404579041122800860290?mg=reno64-wsj.html?dsk=y|newspaper=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]]|date=5 September 2013|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060813/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324324404579041122800860290?mg=reno64-wsj.html%3Fdsk%3Dy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=reuters>{{cite news|last=Toyer|first=Julien|title=Pragmatism may guide politicians as Catalonian separatism flares again|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/09/us-spain-catalonia-idUSBRE9880H320130909|agency=Reuters|accessdate=2013-09-14|archive-date=2013-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914044106/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/09/us-spain-catalonia-idUSBRE9880H320130909|dead-url=no}}</ref>，共有14個非政府组织参与<ref name=wsj />，其路線沿着历史上的奥古斯塔道的路線展开。加泰羅尼亞内政部估计有160万人参与此次活动<ref>{{cite news|title=More than 1 million Catalans form human chain to promote their bid to break away from Spain|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/catalans-in-favor-of-breaking-away-from-spain-form-huge-human-chain-to-advertise-their-cause/2013/09/11/0ce45f06-1afa-11e3-80ac-96205cacb45a_story.html|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=11 September 2013|agency=Associated Press|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912142306/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/catalans-in-favor-of-breaking-away-from-spain-form-huge-human-chain-to-advertise-their-cause/2013/09/11/0ce45f06-1afa-11e3-80ac-96205cacb45a_story.html|archivedate=2013-09-12|accessdate=2019-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

为了完成此次活动，組織者動用了1500辆巴士及30000位志願者<ref name=wsj /><ref>{{cite news|title=Human chain for Catalan independence organized|url=http://www.worldbulletin.net/?aType=haber&ArticleID=117138|newspaper=World Bulletin|date=6 September 2013|accessdate=2013-09-14|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109113955/http://www.worldbulletin.net/?aType=haber&ArticleID=117138|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們也預定了二十架直升機並承包了800位攝影師来拍摄此次活动。

